<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW237966883 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW237966883 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW237966883 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW237966883 BCX8">Qual a estrat&eacute;gia da sua empresa diante dessas mudan&ccedil;as?</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW237966883 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW237966883 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW237966883 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW237966883 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW237966883 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Adaptabilidade e agilidade s&atilde;o compet&ecirc;ncias essenciais para a sobreviv&ecirc;ncia de organiza&ccedil;&otilde;es na Nova Economia. Neste novo cen&aacute;rio, a maneira de fazer neg&oacute;cios, formar talentos, compartilhar valor e exercer a lideran&ccedil;a ser&aacute; </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW237966883 BCX8">muito diferente dos modelos atuais. A acelera&ccedil;&atilde;o dos ciclos de mudan&ccedil;as est&aacute; redefinindo a competitividade, e as empresas precisam se adaptar para futuros cen&aacute;rios. &Eacute; essencial criar e manter propostas de valor que atendam &agrave;s exig&ecirc;ncias e necessidades de clientes, colaboradores e stakeholders.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW237966883 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW237966883 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW237966883 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW237966883 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW237966883 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW130699660 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW130699660 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span>Estruturar uma nova Cultura Inovativa, capacitando colaboradores e vivenciando na pr&aacute;tica m&eacute;todos, ferramentas, formas de pensar e gerar ideias conectadas &agrave;s estrat&eacute;gias do neg&oacute;cio e ao entendimento profundo dos usu&aacute;rios, pode ser a melhor estrat&eacute;gia para as organiza&ccedil;&otilde;es.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW237966883 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW237966883 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW237966883 BCX8"><strong><span class="TextRun SCXW237966883 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW237966883 BCX8">O que &eacute; Design Estrat&eacute;gico?</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW237966883 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></strong></h3>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW237966883 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW237966883 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW237966883 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW237966883 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW130699660 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW130699660 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span>O Design Estrat&eacute;gico &eacute; a resposta &agrave; cultura e compet&ecirc;ncias pr&aacute;ticas necess&aacute;rias para colaboradores e empresas em um mundo em transforma&ccedil;&atilde;o. Ele aborda os desafios do neg&oacute;cio de forma criativa e atenta &agrave;s reais </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW237966883 BCX8">necessidades de clientes, consumidores, colaboradores e stakeholders. Isso implica identificar lacunas, insights e oportunidades alinhadas ao mercado e &agrave;s estrat&eacute;gias da organiza&ccedil;&atilde;o.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW237966883 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="Paragraph SCXW237966883 BCX8"><span class="EOP SCXW237966883 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{"><img src="https://inventta.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Prancheta-1-copia-2-9.png" width="952" height="644"></span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW237966883 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW237966883 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW237966883 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW237966883 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW130699660 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW130699660 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span>Para n&oacute;s, a inova&ccedil;&atilde;o &eacute; o resultado bem-sucedido da transforma&ccedil;&atilde;o de uma proposta de valor, preparando equipes e organiza&ccedil;&otilde;es para um cen&aacute;rio futuro, com novas propostas de valor e entrega.</span></span> <span class="SCXW237966883 BCX8"><span class="WACImageContainer NoPadding DragDrop BlobObject SCXW237966883 BCX8" role="presentation"><span class="EOP SCXW130699660 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<p class="Paragraph SCXW237966883 BCX8"><span class="SCXW237966883 BCX8"><span class="WACImageContainer NoPadding DragDrop BlobObject SCXW237966883 BCX8" role="presentation"><span class="EOP SCXW130699660 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{"><img src="https://inventta.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Prancheta-1-copia-3-6.png" width="795" height="446"></span></span></span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW237966883 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
